com.igeekinc.indelible.indeliblefs.events

Class IndelibleEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.igeekinc.indelible.indeliblefs.events.IndelibleEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CASCollectionEvent, CASServerEvent

    public abstract class IndelibleEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is the base class for Indelible FS events. All Indelible FS events are identified by the EntityID (server) that generated the event, a 64 bit event number and a 64 bit timestamp
